title: Coastal Chat
description:
Wendi Nix, Tom Luginbill, and Trevor Matich discuss this weekend's new BYU v Coastal Carolina matchup, the CFP rankings and Texas and Michigan's coaching issues. Jimbo Fisher also joins the show.
